caption.p: Correlation of F max (left panel) and nonequilibrium work (right panel), W neq, with logBB, TPSA, and logPS for compounds considered in this study ( Table S1) in the case of the CHARMM36 force-field for the DOPC/cholesterol (2:1) membrane model and pulling velocity v = 5 nm/ns ( Table S4).
